                        Passionate Full Stack Web Developer with expertise in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Bootstrap, Tailwind CSS, React.js, PHP, Laravel, Node.js, Express.js, MySQL, and MongoDB. Experienced in designing responsive, user-friendly, and high-performance web applications. Strong problem-solving skills, clean coding practices, and a continuous learning mindset with growing experience in AI-powered development tools.
                    </p>

                    <!-- TECHNICAL SKILLS -->
