                            <span class="resume-project-title">E-Commerce Web Application</span>
                            <span class="resume-project-date">Recent</span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="resume-bullets">
                            <li><span class="resume-highlight">Full Stack Architecture:</span> Formulated full stack logic ensuring secure checkout pipelines, state management, and seamless dynamic product displays.</li>
                            <li><span class="resume-highlight">Responsive Design:</span> Integrated responsive mobile-first UI grids using Bootstrap 5 and Tailwind CSS to guarantee visual consistency on all device viewports.</li>
