                        <ul class="resume-bullets">
                            <li><span class="resume-highlight">Modern Frontend:</span> Designed and developed a premium dark-themed portfolio using React.js and modern visual component systems.</li>
                            <li><span class="resume-highlight">Version Control:</span> Utilized advanced Git workflow and GitHub repos for continuous integration, code auditing, and hosting pipelines.</li>
                        </ul>
